name: EnumerationUtilsTest
description: Unit tests for the EnumerationUtils class, which provides utility methods for working with Enumerations.

test_cases.name: testAsIterableFor
test_cases.description: Tests the asIterable method of EnumerationUtils to ensure it correctly converts an Enumeration to an Iterable.

test_cases.name: testAsIterableForNull
test_cases.description: Tests the asIterable method of EnumerationUtils to ensure it throws a NullPointerException when given a null Enumeration.

test_cases.name: testGetFromEnumeration
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of EnumerationUtils to ensure it correctly retrieves elements from an Enumeration by index and handles out-of-bounds indices.

test_cases.name: testToListWithHashtable
test_cases.description: Tests the toList method of EnumerationUtils to ensure it correctly converts the elements and keys of a Hashtable to Lists.

test_cases.name: testToListWithStringTokenizer
test_cases.description: Tests the toList method of EnumerationUtils to ensure it correctly converts a StringTokenizer to a List.
